                                    <xs:documentation source="autofillkey">SOFWDocs</xs:documentation>
                                    <xs:documentation source="title">Please provide documentation to verify each source of funds or wealth</xs:documentation>
                                    <xs:documentation source="note">We are required to obtain and verify information on the source of funds and source of wealth for prospective investors in order to comply with New Zealand's Anti-Money Laundering and Countering Financing of Terrorism Act 2009.

For examples of types of verification documentation, please select the help button.</xs:documentation>
                                    <xs:documentation source="hint">&lt;h4&gt;Non-exhaustive list of verification documentation&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Employment&lt;/strong&gt;

* Copy of pay slip (or bonus) from within last three months
* Bank statement showing regular income
* IRD documents (e.g. tax return/invoice)
* Employment Contract

&lt;strong&gt;Business proceeds&lt;/strong&gt;

* Copy of latest audited company accounts

&lt;strong&gt;Disposal of business or assets&lt;/strong&gt;

* Copy of latest audited company accounts
* Settlement statement
* Sale and purchase agreement
* Bank statement showing deposit from solicitor's trust account

&lt;strong&gt;Investment income&lt;/strong&gt;

* Copy of investment / savings certificates or contract notes
* Bank statement clearly showing receipt of funds and investment company name
* Signed letter detailing funds from a regulated accountant/solicitor

Investment income documents will need to be supported by evidence of how the investable wealth was previously accumulated

&lt;strong&gt;Superannuation lump sum or annuity/retirement plan payments&lt;/strong&gt;

* Copy of closing statement
* Letter confirming collection

&lt;strong&gt;Insurance / compensation claim&lt;/strong&gt;

* Copy of closing statement
* Letter from insurer confirming claim

&lt;strong&gt;Lottery / betting win&lt;/strong&gt;

* Lotteries Commission

&lt;strong&gt;Inheritance&lt;/strong&gt;

* Grant of Probate (copy of the will) which must include the value of the estate
* Bank statement showing deposit from solicitor's trust account

&lt;strong&gt;Gift&lt;/strong&gt;

* Donor's source of wealth - requirements of evidence as stated above for each individual source of wealth and a letter from the donor confirming details of the gift
* Bank statement showing deposit from solicitor's trust account

&lt;strong&gt;Maturity or surrender of life policy&lt;/strong&gt;

* Copy of closing statement
* Letter from insurer confirming surrender

&lt;strong&gt;Sale of property&lt;/strong&gt;

* Copy of sale and purchase agreement
* Settlement statement
* Bank statement showing deposit from solicitor's trust account
* LINZ information</xs:documentation>
