                                    <xs:documentation source="note">Note, a bank statement is unlikely to be sufficient evidence of source of wealth unless the bank statement identifies where the funds have originated from. A letter from a professional such as an accountant, lawyer or advisor which outlines the source of funds/wealth will be sufficient provided it:
 
